      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor; default acceptance at Gradation 1 applies.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2 the standard does not require explicit iterative convergence error quantification beyond residual monitoring. Residuals dropped six orders of magnitude in all production runs; no further action required."
    },
    {
