      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; nominal inputs with documented sources are sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Blood analog properties sourced from ASTM F1841. Pump geometry from FDA public repository. Input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
    },
