      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; single experimental dataset with documented provenance is acceptable.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark PIV dataset (publicly available, Stewart et al. 2012) used. Sample-to-sample variability analysis not required at MRL 2."
