      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; qualitative equivalency argument in validation report is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Validation conditions span the COU operating envelope (2.5–7.5 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Formal equivalency metric not required at MRL 2; qualitative argument accepted per Table 3 of the standard."
