    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. Decision scope and intended use are fully described in the Requirement node (https://uofa.net/morrison/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) and Claim node (https://uofa.net/morrison/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case).",
